<p>Most of my nightmares consist of running from people<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-200527-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-200527-1')">1</a></sup> at night, and sometimes even in Carolina Beach (this is a real area and I live here, as some of you know). I tried to channel that my-legs-won't-work-fast-enough-help vibe that I get in my dreams. Glad it seems to have worked.</p>
